---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Maw maw Studio"
	description="Learn more about our creative design studio and our approach to spatial design"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<div class="about-content">
		<h2>Our Story</h2>
		<p>
			Maw maw Studio was founded with a vision to create exceptional spatial experiences through innovative design. We combine artistic vision with technical expertise to transform spaces into inspiring environments.
		</p>

		<h2>Our Approach</h2>
		<p>
			We believe in collaborative partnerships and a human-centered design approach. Every project begins with understanding your unique needs and objectives, followed by a thoughtful creative process that brings your vision to life.
		</p>

		<h2>Our Services</h2>
		<div class="services-grid">
			<div class="service">
				<h3>3D Design</h3>
				<p>Creating stunning 3D visualizations and models that bring concepts to life.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="service">
				<h3>Interior Design</h3>
				<p>Crafting beautiful, functional spaces that reflect your style and needs.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="service">
				<h3>Architectural Visualization</h3>
				<p>Producing photorealistic renders of architectural projects and spaces.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="service">
				<h3>Space Planning</h3>
				<p>Optimizing layout and flow to create efficient, harmonious environments.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
		<p>
			We're always excited to take on new challenges and collaborate with forward-thinking clients. If you have a project in mind, we'd love to hear from you.
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2em;
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.service {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}
	.service h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.service p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
</style>